=head1 DESCRIPTION

A structure that contains the information for one performance event
that RUM collects from a user session with your application.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Details => Str

A string containing details about the event.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Id => Str

A unique ID for this event.


=head2 Metadata => Str

Metadata about this event, which contains a JSON serialization of the
identity of the user for this session. The user information comes from
information such as the HTTP user-agent request header and document
interface.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Timestamp => Str

The exact time that this event occurred.


